OL,3,C16-year-old boy charged with murder
OL,4,Cafter 14-year-old shot dead in south
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FA 16-year-old boy has been charged
OL,8,Fwith murder after a 14-year-old boy
OL,9,Fwas fatally shot in south-east London,
OL,10,Fthe Metropolitan Police have said.
OL,12,FEghosa Ogbebor was shot in Woolwich on
OL,13,FApril 2. Emergency services arrived at
OL,14,Faround 3:40pm and found him with
OL,15,Fserious injuries, but he could not be
OL,16,Fsaved and died at the scene.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
