PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775859116
OL,3,C16-year-old boy charged with murder
OL,4,Cafter 14-year-old shot dead in south
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FThe 16-year-old boy was arrested two
OL,8,Fdays after the incident and released
OL,9,Fon bail, but was re-arrested on
OL,10,FThursday. He was charged with murder
OL,11,Fon Friday, according to police.
OL,13,FEghosa's family continue to be
OL,14,Fsupported by specialist officers, the
OL,15,Fforce added, and the investigation
OL,16,Fremains ongoing.
OL,18,FA number of other arrests have been
OL,19,Fmade in connection with the shooting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
