CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775859116
OL,3,C16-year-old boy charged with murder
OL,4,Cafter 14-year-old shot dead in south
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FA different 16-year-old boy and a 19-
OL,8,Fyear-old man were arrested in Woolwich
OL,9,Fon suspicion of murder on April 4. A
OL,10,F46-year-old man was also arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender.
OL,13,FAll three were released on bail.
OL,15,FThe day prior, two boys aged 14 and
OL,16,F16, and an 18-year-old man were
OL,17,Farrested in connection with Eghosa's
OL,18,Fdeath, and have also been bailed while
OL,19,Fenquiries continue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
